A '''shipwomb''' was a facility used to grow and assemble [[Yuuzhan Vong]] ships, analogous to a mechanical [[Shipyard/Legends|shipyard]]. These facilities were usually carved out of the ruins of destroyed or conquered worlds. [[Sernpidal/Legends|Sernpidal]] held one within its remains after that [[Dobido|world's moon]] [[Yo'gand's Core|crashed]] into it. They used [[dovin basal]]s to 'mine' material from a world's [[Star/Legends|sun]].

